00:00:24,750 --> 00:00:29,450
Imagine this scenario: You have 1GB of data that you need to process.

6
00:00:29,450 --> 00:00:33,570
The data is stored in a relational database in your desktop computer which has no problem

7
00:00:33,570 --> 00:00:35,350
