When your data grows from 1 TB to 10TB, and then 100TB,

14
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:02,489
you are again quickly approaching the limits of that computer.

15
00:01:02,489 --> 00:01:09,170
Moreover, you are now asked to feed your application with unstructured data coming from sources

16
00:01:09,170 --> 00:01:14,780
like Facebook, Twitter, RFID readers, sensors, and so on.

17
